OL,3,CRed flags on Guernsey's coastal paths
OL,4,Cmark out unique ant nests
OL,6,FDespite the large numbers, Guernsey
OL,7,Fhas seen a 42% decline in numbers in
OL,8,F30 years.
OL,10,FJulie explained: "A lot of people
OL,11,Fthink ants are a pest if they get in
OL,12,Fyour house but they are important;
OL,13,Fthey're part of Guernsey's
OL,14,Fbiodiversity and they need to be
OL,15,Flooked after.
OL,17,F"As David Attenborough says, these
OL,18,Fspecies have as much right to be on
OL,19,Fthis planet as we do so we all need to
OL,20,Fdo our bit."
